<h2>1. Introduction</h2>
<p>Desco Lead CRM ("we," "our," or "us") operates the Desco Lead CRM platform, a customer relationship management system designed to receive and manage leads from Facebook and Instagram Lead Ads through the Meta Platform.</p>
<p>This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect information obtained through our integration with Meta's Lead Ads platform. By using our service, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

<div class="info-card highlight">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Our Commitment</h4>
  <p>We are committed to protecting your personal data and complying with applicable data protection regulations, including Meta Platform Terms and GDPR principles.</p>
</div>

<h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
<h3>2.1 Data from Facebook Lead Ads</h3>
<p>When a user submits a lead form on Facebook or Instagram, we receive the following information through Meta's Webhook system:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Full Name</strong> — as provided in the lead form</li>
  <li><strong>Phone Number</strong> — as provided in the lead form</li>
  <li><strong>Email Address</strong> — if provided in the lead form</li>
  <li><strong>Form ID</strong> — identifies which lead form was submitted</li>
  <li><strong>Ad ID</strong> — identifies the advertisement source</li>
  <li><strong>LeadGen ID</strong> — Meta's unique identifier for the lead submission</li>
</ul>

<h3>2.2 Technical Data</h3>
<p>We automatically collect certain technical information when our system processes lead data:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Timestamps of when leads are received</li>
  <li>Server logs for debugging and security monitoring</li>
  <li>API interaction records</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
<p>We use collected data exclusively for legitimate business purposes:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Lead Management</strong> — Organizing and tracking incoming business leads</li>
  <li><strong>Customer Communication</strong> — Contacting potential customers who expressed interest</li>
  <li><strong>Business Analytics</strong> — Understanding lead sources and campaign effectiveness</li>
  <li><strong>Internal Notifications</strong> — Sending lead alerts to authorized team members via Telegram</li>
  <li><strong>CRM Operations</strong> — Managing the sales pipeline and customer relationships</li>
</ul>

<div class="info-card">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-ban"></i> What We Do NOT Do</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>We do <strong>not sell</strong> personal data to third parties</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not share</strong> data for advertising purposes</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not use</strong> data for profiling or automated decision-making</li>
    <li>We do <strong>not transfer</strong> data to unauthorized parties</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2>4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
<h3>4.1 Storage</h3>
<p>Your data is stored securely using the following infrastructure:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Database</strong> — PostgreSQL hosted on Supabase with encrypted connections</li>
  <li><strong>Server</strong> — Node.js application hosted on Railway with HTTPS encryption</li>
  <li><strong>Backups</strong> — Automated database backups managed by Supabase</li>
</ul>

<h3>4.2 Security Measures</h3>
<ul>
  <li>All data transmitted over HTTPS/TLS encrypted connections</li>
  <li>Meta Webhook signature verification (X-Hub-Signature-256) using HMAC-SHA256</li>
  <li>Environment variables for sensitive credentials (never hardcoded)</li>
  <li>Authentication required for CRM dashboard access</li>
  <li>Session-based access control with secure cookies</li>
  <li>Role-based access — only authorized administrators can view lead data</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain lead data for the duration necessary to fulfill our business purposes:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Active leads</strong> — retained while the business relationship is active</li>
  <li><strong>Completed leads</strong> — retained for up to 24 months for analytics</li>
  <li><strong>Upon request</strong> — data is deleted within 30 days of a valid deletion request</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We integrate with the following third-party services:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Meta (Facebook/Instagram)</strong> — Lead Ads data source via Webhooks and Graph API</li>
  <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Database hosting and management</li>
  <li><strong>Railway</strong> — Application hosting</li>
  <li><strong>Telegram</strong> — Internal team notifications (lead name and phone only)</li>
</ul>
<p>Each third-party service has its own privacy policy. We encourage you to review them.</p>

