<h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Right to Access</strong> — Request a copy of your stored data</li>
  <li><strong>Right to Rectification</strong> — Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
  <li><strong>Right to Deletion</strong> — Request complete deletion of your data (<a href="/data-deletion">Data Deletion Instructions</a>)</li>
  <li><strong>Right to Restriction</strong> — Request limitation of data processing</li>
  <li><strong>Right to Portability</strong> — Request data in a machine-readable format</li>
  <li><strong>Right to Object</strong> — Object to data processing</li>
</ul>

